                    "section_space_padding_padding_options": "1",
                    "section_space_padding_padding_position": "a:1:{i:0;s:6:\"bottom\";}",
                    "grid_items_0_cta_button": "",
                    "grid_items_1_cta_button": "",
                    "grid_items_0_description": "Mentoring is an important aspect of qBotica’s community support strategy. We offer mentorship to students, young professionals, and aspiring entrepreneurs who are interested in learning technolog and Automation. Our unique mentoring program provides a platform for individuals to gain practical experience, guidance, and support from experienced professionals in the field. The mentoring program is designed to help individuals develop skills and knowledge that will enable them to succeed in their careers and entrepreneurial ventures.\r\n\r\nqBotica also offers internships to students who are interested in gaining practical experience in the field of <a href=\"/resources/agentic-ai-use-cases/intelligent-automation-cross-industry-agentic-ai-use-cases\">Intelligent Automation</a>. The internships provide students with an opportunity to work on real-world projects, learn new skills, and gain exposure to the industry. qBotica has partnerships with several colleges and universities to provide these internship opportunities to students.",
                    "grid_items_1_description": "In addition to mentoring and internships, qBotica also supports the community by partnering with entrepreneur organizations. We collaborate with these organizations to provide support and guidance to entrepreneurs who are working on innovative projects related to robotics and automation. Through these partnerships, qBotica helps entrepreneurs to turn their ideas into reality and to build successful businesses.\r\n\r\nqBotica’s community support initiatives aim to promote innovation and education in the field of robotics and automation. Through mentoring, internships, and partnerships with entrepreneur organizations and college universities, qBotica is helping to build a strong and vibrant community of professionals and entrepreneurs who are working to advance the field of RPA and Intelligent Automation.",
