                {
                  "__component": "acf-sections.unmapped-layout",
                  "layout_type": "about_strategic_highlights_section",
                  "title": "Powering the Next Era of AI-Native Automation",
                  "description": "Qbotica, has joined forces with Kognitos to redefine how businesses approach automation. This partnership brings together Qbotica’s proven expertise in RPA and intelligent automation with Kognitos’ groundbreaking natural language processing (NLP) platform that enables users to automate using plain English no coding required.\n\nTogether, we empower organizations to deploy automation up to 4x faster, reduce manual effort and costs by up to 90%, and significantly improve accuracy and productivity. Clients gain access to Qbotica’s GenAI experts and Kognitos’ AI-native technology to drive innovation across industries.\n\nWith this collaboration, businesses can embrace scalable, adaptive, and future-ready automation that’s simple, powerful, and truly transformative.",
